column4: RT @uofsandiego Wishing our @uofsandiego community a blessed Ash Wednesday. Please join us for Ash Wednesday Masses, either at 12:15 p.m. in Founders Chapel or at 8:00 a.m. or 7:00 p.m. in The Immaculata Parish. https://t.co/IRhTnPR7al
